### Health Check Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json

### Get Drivers Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers
Accept: application/json

### Get Driver Documents Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/DRV-1/documents
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Documents Dashboard Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/documents/dashboard
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Driver Document Endpoint
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/drivers/DRV-1/documents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "type": "cnh",
  "documentNumber": "1234567890",
  "issuingAuthority": "DETRAN",
  "issueDate": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "expirationDate": "2030-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Carteira nacional de habilitação categoria AE"
}
